section.para:
When a USHORT number is used to indicate version, it
        should be treated as though it were a minor version number;
        i.e., all format changes are compatible extensions.

section.literallayout:
ULONG
CalcTableChecksum(ULONG *Table, ULONG Length)
{
ULONG Sum = 0L;
ULONG *Endptr = Table+((Length+3) & ~3) / sizeof(ULONG);

while (Table < EndPtr)
        Sum += *Table++;
return Sum;
}
